{"types":[{"section":"\n{{fr-verb}}\n\n# to [[fear]], be afraid\n#: {{syn|fr|craindre}}\n#: {{uxi|fr|J''''ai peur''' qu'il ne parte.|I '''am afraid''' that he will leave.}}\n#: {{uxi|fr|J''''ai peur''' de me tromper.|t=I '''am afraid''' to make a mistake.}}\n#: {{uxi|fr|Tous mes amis '''ont peur''' de mon père.|All my friends '''are afraid''' of my father.}}\n#* {{quote-text|fr|year=2018|author=Zaz|title=Résigne-moi\n|passage=J''''ai peur''' qu' tu t'en ailles en m' laissant sans bruit.}}\n\n====Usage notes====\n* {{m-self|fr|avoir peur}} {{m|fr|que}} takes the subjunctive and, in formal language, the meaningless \"expletive\" {{m|fr|ne}} which does not negate the verb.\n*: {{uxi|fr|J'ai peur qu'il (ne) fasse une erreur|t=I am afraid he will make a mistake.}}\n* {{m|fr|très|t=very}} may intervene between the verb and {{m|fr|peur}}, despite the fact that {{m|fr|peur}} is a noun. This was once [[proscribe]]d but is now accepted.\n\n====Conjugation====\n* see {{m|fr|avoir}}\n\n","alt":[],"syn":["craindre"],"type":"verb","forms":[{"mod":"inf","aux":["avoir"],"pronom":false}],"html":"<p><span class=\"headword-line\"><strong class=\"Latn headword\" lang=\"fr\"><a href=\"/wiki/avoir#French\" title=\"avoir\">avoir</a> <a href=\"/wiki/peur#French\" title=\"peur\">peur</a></strong></span>\n</p><ol><li>to <a href=\"/wiki/fear\" title=\"fear\">fear</a>, be afraid\n<dl><dd><span class=\"nyms synonym\"><span class=\"defdate\">Synonym:</span> <span class=\"Latn\" lang=\"fr\"><a href=\"/wiki/craindre#French\" title=\"craindre\">craindre</a></span></span></dd>\n<dd><span class=\"h-usage-example\"><i class=\"Latn mention e-example\" lang=\"fr\">J'<b>ai peur</b> qu'il ne parte.</i> ― <span class=\"e-translation\">I <b>am afraid</b> that he will leave.</span></span></dd>\n<dd><span class=\"h-usage-example\"><i class=\"Latn mention e-example\" lang=\"fr\">J'<b>ai peur</b> de me tromper.</i> ― <span class=\"e-translation\">I <b>am afraid</b> to make a mistake.</span></span></dd>\n<dd><span class=\"h-usage-example\"><i class=\"Latn mention e-example\" lang=\"fr\">Tous mes amis <b>ont peur</b> de mon père.</i> ― <span class=\"e-translation\">All my friends <b>are afraid</b> of my father.</span></span></dd></dl>\n<ul><li><div class=\"citation-whole\"><span class=\"cited-source\"><span class=\"None\" lang=\"und\"><b>2018</b></span>, Zaz, <cite>Résigne-moi</cite>:</span><dl><dd><div class=\"h-quotation\"><span class=\"Latn e-quotation cited-passage\" lang=\"fr\">J'<b>ai peur</b> qu' tu t'en ailles en m' laissant sans bruit.</span><dl><dd><small>(please <a href=\"/wiki/Wiktionary:Quotations#Adding_translations_to_quotations\" title=\"Wiktionary:Quotations\">add an English translation</a> of this quotation)</small></dd></dl></div></dd></dl></div></li></ul></li></ol><div class=\"mw-heading mw-heading4\"><h4 id=\"Usage_notes\">Usage notes</h4><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=avoir_peur&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Usage notes\"><span>edit</span></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></div><ul><li><i class=\"Latn mention\" lang=\"fr\"><strong class=\"selflink\">avoir peur</strong></i> <i class=\"Latn mention\" lang=\"fr\"><a href=\"/wiki/que#French\" title=\"que\">que</a></i> takes the subjunctive and, in formal language, the meaningless \"expletive\" <i class=\"Latn mention\" lang=\"fr\"><a href=\"/wiki/ne#French\" title=\"ne\">ne</a></i> which does not negate the verb.\n<dl><dd><span class=\"h-usage-example\"><i class=\"Latn mention e-example\" lang=\"fr\">J'ai peur qu'il (ne) fasse une erreur</i> ― <span class=\"e-translation\">I am afraid he will make a mistake.</span></span></dd></dl></li>\n<li><i class=\"Latn mention\" lang=\"fr\"><a href=\"/wiki/tr%C3%A8s#French\" title=\"très\">très</a></i> <span class=\"mention-gloss-paren annotation-paren\">(</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-double-quote\">“</span><span class=\"mention-gloss\">very</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-double-quote\">”</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-paren annotation-paren\">)</span> may intervene between the verb and <i class=\"Latn mention\" lang=\"fr\"><a href=\"/wiki/peur#French\" title=\"peur\">peur</a></i>, despite the fact that <i class=\"Latn mention\" lang=\"fr\"><a href=\"/wiki/peur#French\" title=\"peur\">peur</a></i> is a noun. This was once <a href=\"/wiki/proscribe\" title=\"proscribe\">proscribed</a> but is now accepted.</li></ul><div class=\"mw-heading mw-heading4\"><h4 id=\"Conjugation\">Conjugation</h4><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=avoir_peur&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Conjugation\"><span>edit</span></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></div>","trans":["to fear, be afraid"]}],"title":"avoir peur","id":"1124011","audios":[{"name":"Fr-avoir-peur.ogg","url":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/6/6d/Fr-avoir-peur.ogg"},{"name":"LL-Q150 (fra)-LoquaxFR-avoir peur.wav","url":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/5/52/LL-Q150_%28fra%29-LoquaxFR-avoir_peur.wav"}],"ipas":["/a.vwaʁ pœʁ/"],"pronunSection":"\n* {{fr-IPA}}\n* {{audio|fr|Fr-avoir-peur.ogg}}\n* {{audio|fr|LL-Q150 (fra)-LoquaxFR-avoir peur.wav}}\n\n","pronunHtml":"<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Wiktionary:International_Phonetic_Alphabet\" title=\"Wiktionary:International Phonetic Alphabet\">IPA</a><sup>(<a href=\"/wiki/Appendix:French_pronunciation\" title=\"Appendix:French pronunciation\">key</a>)</sup>: <span class=\"IPA\">/a.vwaʁ pœʁ/</span></li>\n<li><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r50165410\">.mw-parser-output .k-player .k-attribution{visibility:hidden}</style><table class=\"audiotable\" style=\"\"><tbody><tr><td>Audio<span class=\"ib-colon qualifier-colon\">:</span></td><td class=\"audiofile\"><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><span><audio id=\"mwe_player_0\" controls=\"\" preload=\"none\" data-mw-tmh=\"\" class=\"